{"id": "1374071354546192548", "channel_id": "1373674189994725386", "type": 0, "author_id": "776811138984706089", "author_name": "wild_pansy", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得ui不要改動比較好已經習慣現在的ui了而且我也並不覺得混亂\n你現在所給予的參考圖1看起來在美術上能更好地發揮但卻會減少便利性畫面占比太大了視覺動線也很複雜我還是喜歡簡單一點\n2鑰令來源看上去很雜亂但我個人覺得實際上並不會 因為獲取條件綁定在完成故事上所以實際上很直覺而且為了統一鑰令去隨意添加角色劇情或更動我認為更容易出事\n參考圖4我認為未來可以試試看但目前內容過少的情況下這樣做也是在複雜化介面而已\n以上僅僅為我的看法", "timestamp": "2025-05-19T17:08:59.935000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1373674189994725386", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一些便利性方面的建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1374072155112734851", "channel_id": "1373674189994725386", "type": 19, "author_id": "776811138984706089", "author_name": "wild_pansy", "author_bot": false, "content": "通常攸關遊戲建議都會比較少去做回應不然應該很容易跟之前一樣炎上但我覺得作為開發者他們是一定會看的", "timestamp": "2025-05-19T17:12:10.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1374069347118747680", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1373674189994725386", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "一些便利性方面的建议", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1374083422116643086", "channel_id": "1374083422116643086", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi, \n\nAs a newer player, playing ARC 2 content is really hard without any unit above level 70. \n\nIt's not that easy for a new player to get refined gnosis. I still haven't unlocked 1 yet and I'm 2.5 months in.\n\nCould you please add one of them to the battle pass? \n\nMay free battle pass gives you 8 fragments and paid one adds another 16 fragments?\n\nThis would greatly help those player that don't use blue units in ARC 2 (the 3 other realms - you know that also are in this game) survive in ARC 2. \n\nThank you!", "timestamp": "2025-05-19T17:56:57.068000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-19T17:58:28.773000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1374083422582079569", "filename": "Untitled.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 457172, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1374083422116643086/1374083422582079569/Untitled.png?ex=69cc0ae9&is=69cab969&hm=38f2732bfc84661301d6f842f64cc2dfbb6e9c141d93c81995d732e5d5b658be&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1374083422116643086", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Refined Gnosis in Battle Pass?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1373987433888088146", "channel_id": "1373987433888088146", "type": 0, "author_id": "330799408340008960", "author_name": "lucchi018", "author_bot": false, "content": "During the Chinese New Year period, there was a mini event about editing pics with CNY decorations. And now with the announcement of skins, it got me thinking.\n In some gacha games i've played (example Cookie Run, Saint Seiya Awakening etc) once in a while, they would make skin contests, usually the prizes were in game currency and said skin (sometimes merch).\n I think these types of contests are a net positive for the game bc of the influx of fanart being posted on social medias and a sign of a thriving relationship between the playerbase and devs.", "timestamp": "2025-05-19T11:35:31.691000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1373987433888088146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Possibility of skin contests one?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
